io.card.payment
Class LocalizableStrings

java.lang.Object
  io.card.payment.LocalizableStrings

public final class LocalizableStrings
extends Object

String constants available for localizing. To localize, supply a strings.xml file targeted at the appropriate language with values defined for these keys. Currently, localization is only supported for the scan API.

Version:
2.2
